snippet.title: PIGS are the NEW TOP FUNNY ANIMALS! - LAUGH NOW!
snippet.description:
Pigs are the new top funny animals! Just look how hilarious and cute these pig videos are! Animal videos are the best entertainment because animals never fail to make us laugh! Just look how all these pigs and micro pigs play, fail, behave, make funny sounds, play with dogs, react,... So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!

The content in this compilation is licensed and used with authorization of the rights holder. If you have any questions about compilation or clip licensing, please contact us: tigerlicensing@gmail.com

For more funny videos & pictures visit and like our Facebook page:
